{"tid":778811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"滬黑心疫苗苦主上訪　斥維權難過登天","createTime":"2018-08-14T03:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T06:08:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9135d8045590ab998d4f7f901217eb4f7202130b","tid":778811,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:18:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180814/20475912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F20475912&d=8wRfes4BNiqzHQc1cLrktsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a4d49d32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F20475912&h=96f4cebf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180814/20475912</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月14日 <br />\n<br />\n滬黑心疫苗苦主上訪　斥維權難過登天<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180814/large/a1303a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180814%2Flarge%2Fa1303a.gif&h=27b730e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■譚華昨到國家信訪局上訪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地問題疫苗禍害全國民眾，連日來許多受影響的苦主湧北京上訪。昨早又有一批疫苗受害者到國家信訪局上訪。其中譚華原是上海復旦大學MBA畢業生，4年前因接種懷疑有問題的瘋狗疫苗而出現嚴重後遺症，多年來維權不果，更曾遭當局禁錮毆打，最後更被迫逃離上海。她近日因吉林長春長生假疫苗事件而與其他苦主認識，並一同到北京上訪。<br />\n<br />\n譚華把在國家信訪局排隊等候時所拍的影片上載到Twitter，驚見有大批因着不同原因上訪的訪民聚集，隨後在場訪民人數更達上千人。她發佈走訪國家信訪局見聞，直言維權難過登天。她說：「外面排隊4小時，裏面接着排隊幾小時。權力壟斷下的苦難民眾，把希望寄託在最後一根稻草。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180814/large/a1303b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180814%2Flarge%2Fa1303b.gif&h=a9383702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■上千名不同原因上訪者昨在國家信訪局外大排長龍。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「把希望寄託在最後一根稻草」<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者電話訪問時表示，4年前因接種懷疑有問題的瘋狗疫苗而出現突發性耳聾、癲癇等嚴重後遺症，她與母親因為維權而遭受到當局迫害，不但被毆打至遍體瘀傷及手指骨折，更被長期非法拘禁累計200多天。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，上訪主要提3點要求，第一要求當局遵守國家主席習近平對疫苗事件下達的「以人為本、救人優先」的指導精神，對於未有治療成功的孩子及受害人，根據情況來幫助他們的治療費和生活費；第二要求當局公平公正公開處理他們的診斷結果；第三是要求當局落實對問題疫苗受害人的賠償及保障政策。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n河馬牙力驚人可咬穿鱷魚"},{"pid":"b19aba5cf4d0ebcd73c848fb48bbdfba9c591bc0","tid":778811,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:20:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a502b7de6f9c18653322babac890a122f76e0b7","tid":778811,"uid":179810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:35:40.000Z","msg":"黨會幫你解決問題 放心<br />\n縱做鬼也幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d11636fcc2a360ed94068a05532fa54ddbda287","tid":778811,"uid":13303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上海學咩人搞事呀經濟好就得"},{"pid":"584cb8b2626688016c98459d6730e8740069da67","tid":778811,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:40:53.000Z","msg":"只要攪好經濟, 比人感覺國家向上就得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大頭奶粉單野都係咁處理"},{"pid":"0f9c835d481ee9bd0110018974fab1f5c2d94307","tid":778811,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a502b7de6f9c18653322babac890a122f76e0b7","tid":778811,"uid":179810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:35:40.000Z","msg":"黨會幫你解決問題 放心<br />\n縱做鬼也幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:45:06.000Z","msg":"黨疼國愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca1316adf11d3ecb472663716af4064037ad902","tid":778811,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:46:33.000Z","msg":"維權也瘋狂"},{"pid":"8a2331b9600a2cc1d1c5b7a0d23dfa1ba6743ee7","tid":778811,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:48:31.000Z","msg":"因為冇選票"},{"pid":"988ac59e98254b66ca07b450dcba92a0deec5390","tid":778811,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:48:55.000Z","msg":"去美國大使館微博喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634619ab05b01867aef62d114cc5a73cd7f5a676","tid":778811,"uid":165012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"鄰國的事不容許我們説三道四"},{"pid":"906bf9b73a3435055868c868df5a9d050f91d9d8","tid":778811,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:08:58.000Z","msg":"5毛:不喜歡中國的人可以離開中國"}]}